<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,316,1922,1946]" pageId="3" pageNumber="578">FIGURES 1–5.</emphasis>
(1) Habitus of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Eldredge" authorityYear="2022" box="[478,727,1922,1946]" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Myrmecoagria" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="578" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hoebekei">
<emphasis box="[478,727,1922,1946]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="578">Myrmecoagria hoebekei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, male holotype. (2) Head and pronotum of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Eldredge" authorityYear="2022" box="[1181,1430,1922,1946]" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Myrmecoagria" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="578" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hoebekei">
<emphasis box="[1181,1430,1922,1946]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="578">Myrmecoagria hoebekei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, male holotype. (3) Paratype labels, female. (4) Holotype labels, male. (5) Habitus of host pinned with paratype female.
